<ul style="color: #ccc; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; padding-left: 20px; margin: 0;">
<li><strong></strong> Managed a <strong>$81,735.61</strong> hardware budget, picking Dell and Square systems for their reliability and long-term support.</li>
<li><strong></strong> Used identical hardware across the facility to make maintenance easier and ensure any employee can use any station.</li>
<li><strong></strong> Chose ruggedized terminal nodes for the warehouse areas to handle the dust and high-intensity use of a bike manufacturing floor.</li>
</ul>
